<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"><meta name='copyright' content='pavilan'><meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no"><meta name="author" content="Trenova School Support Centre"> <meta name="keyword" content="School Development Plan, School Owners Forum, Edu-Business Strategist, Association of Proprietors, School Administrators, NAPPS, Education Business Strategist, Educational Marketer, Consulting, School Growth, School Owners, Management Consulting"><meta name="description" content="TreNova support school growth, creates and sells businesses; provides training and business grant; publish learning support contents for private schools"><title>Reading Ambassador</title><link rel="icon" type="image/favicon.png" href="favicon.ico"><link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"><link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin><link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"> <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous"> <link href="https://code.ionicframework.com/ionicons/2.0.1/css/ionicons.min.css" rel="stylesheet"> <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/font-awesome.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="css/slicknav.min.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="css/reset.min.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="css/custom.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="style.min.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="css/responsive.css"> <style>p{font-size:1.3em !important;}@media only screen and (max-width: 600px){.lib-video{width:100%; height:300px;}.header-flex{width:100%;}.custom-form-container{width:100%;}.youtube-frame{width:100%; height:300px !important;}}</style></head><body id="bg"><div id="page" class="site boxed-layout"> <div class="preeloader"><div class="preloader-spinner"></div></div><?php include "includes/header.php" ?><div class='container-fluid'><div class="row bg-dark" style='background-image:url("img/children/ambassador.jpg"); background-size:cover;'><div class="container"> <div class='col-sm-12 d-flex align-items-center'> <div class='px-3 py-5'> <h4 class='mb-3'>Make up to </h4> <h1 style='font-size:5em; color:#FE9F00;' class='mb-3'>₦500k</h1> <h4 class='mb-3'>Per month working as a</h4> <h1 style='background-color:#FE9F00;' class='fw-bold px-4 py-2'> LEARNNOVA AMBASSADOR</h1> <h4 class='mt-3'>Join over 13,000 Ambassadors in our network</h4> </div></div></div></div></div><div class="container"> <div class="row d-flex align-items-center"> <div class="col-sm-6"> <div class='px-3 mt-3'> <p> The rate of failure among learners in external examinations is increasing at a rapid rate in our country. Many research experts have attributed this sudden decadence to lack of sufficient participation of learners in the learning process and reading as been identified as on of the major ways to get learners participate in the learning process. In other to contribute our bit towards reducing this ugly trend, our organisation, TreNova School Support Centre is supporting the establishment of reading culture in our schools. </p></div></div><div class="col-sm-6"> <img src="img/children/read_5.png" alt=""class="img-fluid " > </div></div></div><div class="container"> <div class="row d-flex align-items-center"> <div class="col-sm-6 order-sm-1 order-2"> <img src="img/children/read_6.png" alt="" class="img-fluid"> </div><div class="col-sm-6 order-sm-2 order-1"> <div class='px-3'> <p> This we do by offering private school a customisable e-reading library that contains about 450 reading books for learners between age 3 – 17 years old and also allowed each school to add their staff e-notes and other reading materials </p></div></div></div></div><div class="container"> <div class="row d-flex align-items-center"> <div class="col-sm-6"> <div class='px-3'> <p> Access to this platform avails each school an opportunity to enrol their learners into the ‘20-Minute-a-Day-Reading’ Initiative tagged ‘I Can Read’. The learner’s participation in the I Can Read systematic and regular reading program will offer them the opportunity to read about 10 books per term and about 30 every academic year. </p></div></div><div class="col-sm-6"> <img src="img/children/read_7.png" alt="" class="img-fluid"> </div></div></div><div class="container"> <div class="row d-flex align-items-center"> <div class="col-sm-12"> <h4 class='py-5 custom-black'> The systematic reading program is designed to help each child achieve the following: </h4> </div></div></div><div class="container"> <div class="row d-flex align-items-center"> <div class="col-sm-6"> <div class='d-flex py-3'> <div class='px-4'><h1 style='color:#6FB71D;'>1</h1></div><div> <h4 class="custom-black">Fosters reading culture:</h4> <p>The platform helps the learners read and exposes them to a vast number of new words (1.8 million words in each school year, actually!). This exposure increases the chances of a pupil scoring above the 90th percentile in standardized tests. </p></div></div><div class='d-flex py-3'> <div class='px-4'><h1 style='color:#6FB71D;'>2</h1></div><div> <h4 class="custom-black">Improves their ability to assimilate:</h4> <p> It has been shown that regular reading improves brain connectivity, ability to focus and concentrate. </p></div></div><div class='d-flex py-3'> <div class='px-4'><h1 style='color:#6FB71D;'>3</h1></div><div> <h4 class="custom-black">Improves their English language and social skills: </h4> <p> Consistent exposure to new words on the platform will improve the pupil’s social skills, communication skills, vocabulary, comprehension and dictions. </p></div></div><div class='d-flex py-3'> <div class='px-4'><h1 style='color:#6FB71D;'>4</h1></div><div> <h4 class="custom-black">Improves their creativity:</h4> <p> The platform and consistent reading in general will spark their imagination and stimulates their curiosity thus helping them to grow into innovative citizens. </p></div></div><div class='d-flex py-3'> <div class='px-4'><h1 style='color:#6FB71D;'>5</h1></div><div> <h4 class="custom-black">Improves the overall learning outcome and brand perception:</h4> <p> Regular reading has been known to increase learners’ intelligence quotient and learning outcome. This in turn will definitely promote school’s brand perception and improves brand awareness. </p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6 d-flex align-items-center"> <img src="img/children/read_4.png" alt="" class="d-block img-fluid mx-auto d-none d-sm-block"> </div></div></div><div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-sm-12"> <h4 class='pt-5 pb-3 custom-black'> What is Your Role as a Reading Ambassador? </h4> <p> Your role is to show the benefits and impact of regular reading in achieving improved leaning outcome to private school owners and help them to implement e-reading library in exchange for a termly income. To begin to take advantage of this OPPORTUNITY, the first step is to complete the expression of interest form below and prepare for our selection interview. </p></div></div></div><div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-sm-12"> <h4 class='pt-5 pb-3 custom-black'> Your benefits as a Learnnova Reading Ambassador: </h4> <div class="d-flex"> <div class='px-3'> <i class="icon ion-checkmark-circled" style='color:#6FB71D; font-size:2em;'></i> </div><div> <p class='mb-5'> For every school you help to implement the e-library, <b class='text-danger'>you are paid 30% of their termly usage fee</b>. </p></div></div><div class="d-flex"> <div class='px-3'> <i class="icon ion-checkmark-circled" style='color:#6FB71D; font-size:2em;'></i> </div><div> <p class='mb-5'> Opportunity to become a School Growth Consultant </p></div></div><div class="d-flex"> <div class='px-3'> <i class="icon ion-checkmark-circled" style='color:#6FB71D; font-size:2em;'></i> </div><div> <p class='mb-5'> Access to free branded materials </p></div></div><div class="d-flex"> <div class='px-3'> <i class="icon ion-checkmark-circled" style='color:#6FB71D; font-size:2em;'></i> </div><div> <p class='mb-5'> Free trainings </p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="custom-form px-3 py-3 mb-5 "><div class="container text-center mb-4"> <h3 style='color:#6fb71d;'>Expression of Interest Form</h3></div><form class='container' id="ambassador-form" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data"><p class='fw-bold mb-3'>This is an expression of interest and application for consideration for career in Motivating Private Schools to Implement Regular Reading Culture. It does not obligate you to proceed further. </p><p class="mb-4 fw-bold mb-3">If this is a joint application then each individual should complete the form.Please answer every question carefully and to the best of your ability.</p><div class="row"> <div class="col-sm-4 col-12 mb-3"> <label for="" class="form-label fw-bold text-uppercase">YOUR FIRST NAME</label> <input type="text" name="firstname" class="form-control py-3 border-0 px-3 lemon-bg" id=""> </div><div class="col-sm-4 col-12 mb-3"> <label for="" class="form-label fw-bold text-uppercase">SURNAME</label> <input type="text" name="surname" class="form-control py-3 px-3 lemon-bg border-0" id=""> </div><div class="col-sm-4 col-12 mb-3"> <label for="" class="form-label fw-bold text-uppercase">OTHER NAMES</label> <input type="text" name="other_names" class="form-control px-3 py-3 lemon-bg border-0" id=""> </div></div><div class="row"> <div class="col-12 mb-3"> <label for="" class="form-label fw-bold text-uppercase">E-MAIL</label> <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control py-3 px-3 lemon-bg border-0" id=""> </div></div><div class="row"> <div class="col-12 mb-3"> <label for="" class="form-label fw-bold text-uppercase">ADDRESS</label> <i